                    <div class="feature-text">
                        <span class="feature-num">02</span>
                        <h3 class="feature-title" style="color:#4fc3f7;">REAL-TIME REDACTION</h3>
                        <p class="feature-desc">Emails, phone numbers, SSNs, credit cards — detected and replaced before they reach the provider. Works on streamed output too, chunk by chunk.</p>
