 My SSN is <span class="t-bright">123-45-6789</span>       My SSN is <span class="t-blue">&lt;protected:ssn&gt;</span>
 Card: <span class="t-bright">4111-1111-1111-1111</span>   Card: <span class="t-blue">&lt;protected:creditcard&gt;</span></pre>
                    </div>
